[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "レスナちゃん、久しぶり！\nすっごく会いたかったよー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00040",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "久しぶりだね、イザナちゃん！\n私が学園に入学する前からだから……半年以上ぶりかな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00041",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "そうだよ！　夏休みとか冬休みは帰って来るかなって\n思ったのに、ぜんぜん帰って来てくれないんだもん！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00042",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "ずっと会えなくて寂しかったから、\nアタシから会いに来ちゃった！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00043",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "イザナちゃん……！\n私もイザナちゃんに会いたかったよ～！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00044",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "えへへ。突然会いに来ちゃったけど、\n今日はアタシと一緒に過ごしてくれる……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00045",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "うん！　イザナちゃんは王都に来るの、初めてだよね。\n案内するよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00046",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "わーい！　ありがとうレスナちゃん！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00047",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "それにしても、王都って本当に人が多いんだね！\nアタシたちの村とは違うって、ハンマーも驚いてるよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00048",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "私も、初めて来た時は驚いたし戸惑ったよ。\n不良っぽい方にぶつかっちゃったりもして……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00049",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "えっ！\n大丈夫だった？　ハンマーする？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00050",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "ううん！　大丈夫だよ！　見た目で怖いなって\n思っちゃったけど、優しい先輩だったから！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00051",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "ソフィー先輩という方で、同じ錬金術科の生徒として\n色々お世話になってるんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00052",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "錬金術科ってなにするの？\n生徒みんなで錬金釜を使って混ぜたり？　こねたり？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00053",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "調合実習はもちろん、その完成度を競ったり、\n調合品使用可能のバトルロイヤルとかもしたよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00054",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "バトルロイヤル！？　もしかして、錬金術って\n武術とか剣術の仲間だったりした……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00055",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "あとは、他の学校の生徒さんとの交流もあったり……\n文化祭も力が入っていて、とっても楽しかったんだ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00056",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "色々あったんだねー。\nいいなあ、すっごく楽しそう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00057",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "イザナちゃんは、最近どう？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00058",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "アタシかぁ……うーん。\n普通、かな？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00059",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "勉強して、ハンマーして、おうちのお手伝いして……\n代わり映えのない日常って感じ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00060",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "特別なお祭りとか大きな事件とかもないから、\n村は相変わらずで、ちょっと退屈かな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00061",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "そっか……\nでも、平和なのが一番だと思うよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00062",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "うん！　平和が一番、だよね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00063",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "でも……何か、面白いこと起きないかなぁ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00064",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ちょっと、そこのあなた",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00065",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "……え、アタシ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00066",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ええ、あなたですわ。かわいい耳のあなた",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00067",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "わたくしの下へいらっしゃいな。\n光り輝くスターの座が、あなたを待っていますわ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00068",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "え？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00069",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "えーっ！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00070",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "イザナ・ココシュカ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana Kokoschka",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "レスナの幼馴染で、ハンマーが大好きな獣人の少女。\nレスナに会うため、遥々王都へやって来た",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]